      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be fully roadworthy. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dents, areas of rust on the lower panels, and significant paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin has seen heavy use; the upholstery is torn in several places, and some of the interior trim is missing or damaged. Mechanically, the engine starts but runs roughly and has a persistent oil leak, while the transmission occasionally slips when shifting. Additionally, the air conditioning is non-functional and the tires are near the end of their tread life. This car is being sold strictly as-is and would be best suited as a project vehicle or for parts.",
