      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power unit. This high-revving engine remains crisp with smooth double-VANOS variable valve timing actuation and highly responsive individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement plates, mitigating the platform's inherent structural fatigue points. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers for improved lateral stability and dampening. While displaying a light patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain excellent, offering a tactile and visceral driving experience.",
